  "text": "is modeled as a Markov chain containing transition probabilities P (l ki+1 |l ki ) of all tracklets in \u0393 k [CITATION_1] . The transition probability P (l j |l i ) is computed using probabilities of appearance feature P a (l i \u2192 l j ) and motion feature P m (l i \u2192 l j ).",
